Chilean Derivatives Law ‘Urgent’ Given Peso Rise, Correa Says

-- B y   R a n d y   W o o d s
-- 
2011-02-28T19:51:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/chilean-derivatives-law-urgent-given-peso-rise-correa-says.html
Chile’s proposed new law on
derivatives is “urgent” given the appreciation of the
currency, Pablo Correa, the finance ministry’s capital markets
coordinator, told reporters today in Santiago.  The bill could be implemented in the second half of this
year, Correa said.  To contact the reporter responsible on this story:
